{"tid":42750,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"親戚個仔入左中大工程 琴日食飯喺到串串貢","createTime":"2016-12-17T03:19:23.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-24T04:13:22.000Z","uid":33631,"like":67,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"10832bd70cfaf8b785e893053b28067b17bfbb5e","tid":42750,"uid":33631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T03:19:23.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟琴晚同班親戚做冬<br />\n有個親戚個仔(姐係我表弟)入左中大工程<br />\n個親戚親開始周圍宣揚<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:親戚<br />\n<br />\n親戚：鍵騎，你係咪讀工程架？呀賢仔(我表弟)今年都入左工程系喎，得閒指教下佢喇<br />\n我：恭喜晒喎<br />\n親戚：哈哈，多謝。係呢，你讀邊間「腰」嘅工程系架？<br />\n我：科大囉。<br />\n親戚：科大？邊到嚟架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我個仔讀<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中</span></span>大工程喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我：好犀利喎(純粹應酬下佢)。咁你個仔dse幾多分？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n親戚：errrrr....好似21分<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咩？我dse 24分喎。<br />\n親戚：errrrr.....<br />\n我：你個仔得21分？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我個frd讀city bba都23分啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />叫你個仔努力讀書啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">三大最低分。嶺大分數，三大名氣，中大工程幫到你</span></span><br />\n<br />\n之後佢就冇再出過聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4bda40349e533f9360290ac97706e1baf3c024c","tid":42750,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T03:25:23.000Z","msg":"Ching Ho ball"},{"pid":"a317931fae945b0ac858b71f66682b87ca97ffaf","tid":42750,"uid":1773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0